reviewText: Bought this for my autistic son, only thing he wanted for Christmas. Opened the package and it was broken. My son had a meltdown. Merry Christmas to us!
The video plays perfectly well. My son loves it just like me. Thank you for having this in your inventory.

From the sea level desert of Africa to the 17,000' mountain pass in Tibet, the Too Tyred Tour prevailed through sun, sand, wind, rain and snow.  This video illustrates the enormous personal challenge in a tour of this magnitude and inspires one to consider the possibilities.
